title: Expedia and Wotif's Routehappy can tell you which flight will be the happiest
text:
Expedia and Wotif's Routehappy can te... Expedia and Wotif's Routehappy can tell you which flight will be the happiest 5 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
The Routehappy rankings system will give Expedia and Wotif customers the ability to easily tell whether one flight is superior to another. By now, most Australians know that if they get on a Qantas flight from Sydney to Melbourne, it is likely to be a more premium experience than a flight on low-cost arm Jetstar, just as a Virgin Australia flight will include more frills than a flight at its budget arm, Tigerair Australia.   Sydney Morning Herald.
